soon.details: Route is planned to exist and is a work in progress

star.details: Route is very stable and is NOT expected to change

baby.details: New route but expected to be a stable route

boom.details: Route may change, has recently changed, maybe brand new, and/or underconstruction

confused.details: The present past and/or future of this route is not clear

broken_heart.details: Route is expected to break or already is broken

seedling.details: Duplicate Route, another route exists that you should be using

hourglass.details: Known to be a slow route

skull.details: Endpoint is deprecated and will soon be removed

wrench.details: Work is being performed against route

construction.details: Work is being performed against route

turtle.details: Route often is slow to respond

blue_book.details: Contains data listings and/or bulk data

busts_in_silhouette.details: Duplicate or near duplicate of another route
